00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:29,980
=You Are My Hero=

19
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 30=

20
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,960
How is that girl doing?

21
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:40,320
She’s much calmer now.

22
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:41,840
The staff of
the rehabilitation department

23
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,880
are making a

24
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:43,920
training plan for her.

