00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,400
Lift it up with your hand.

26
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,320
See.

27
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,760
This is 1000 cc.

28
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,080
