32
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,000
Are you saying

33
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,400
that it was all mental

34
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,880
when my hand was shaking?

35
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,400
I think it is.

36
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,440
You are mentally convinced

37
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,400
that the surgery would

38
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,680
have a negative impact on

39
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:16,560
the strength and stability

40
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:18,200
of your hands.

41
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,240
You’ve been giving yourself

42
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,640
such a message.

43
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,560
You care a lot about it

44
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,120
and you are eager to recover.

45
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,480
So when you picked up the gun,

46
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:28,400
your hand would shake automatically.

47
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:29,920
But look,

48
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,680
when you were
in the concert hall yesterday,

49
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:32,680
you still had the instinct.

50
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,600
You still had a lot of strength.

51
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,960
From now on,

52
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,640
the most important thing is

53
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,600
to stop thinking about your hands.

54
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:45,160
Just relax, all right?

55
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,360
Put your hands here.

56
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,400
Why?

57
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,440
Except for keeping your mind relaxed,

58
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:55,520
it’s also important

59
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:56,800
to keep your muscle relaxed.

60
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,000
Your hands are going to hold the gun.

61
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:01,000
You need to protect a lot of people.

62
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,520
You can’t get hurt again.

63
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,560
Let me give you a massage, too.

64
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:07,800
I don’t need it.

65
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,440
The surgeon’s hands are more valuable.

66
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,680
Come on.

67
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,120
Xia.

68
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,520
I found an experienced master

69
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,320
and fixed the camera for you.

70
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,640
It’s fixed?

71
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,600
