72
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,800
He stocked up on some lenses.

73
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,960
Where did you find

74
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:36,880
such an experienced master?

75
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:41,120
