76
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,920
Go ahead and try it.

77
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:43,720
Okay, I’ll try it.

78
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,760
Thank you.

79
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,560
Song, well...

80
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:55,880
I also have

81
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,600
an old Leica camera.

82
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,120
Ask the master

83
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,480
and see if he can also

84
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,560
fix it for me.

85
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,800
He only helps Xia.

86
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,800
He won’t fix it for you.

87
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,600
Why not?

88
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,800
Captain Shu got it done.

89
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,200
I forgot.

90
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,720
Xia...

91
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:16,830
I...

92
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,760
How did Shu Wenbo get

93
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:18,680
my camera?

94
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,040
I... He...

95
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,480
It’s not him, I...

96
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,200
Actually...

97
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,720
I’m asking you that how he got it?

98
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,240
I stole it, Xia.

99
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:26,920
You...!

100
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,640
Xia.

101
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:28,560
I don’t think you should

102
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:29,560
blame Captain Shu.

103
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,080
He is just worried

104
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,000
that he can’t fix it by himself.

105
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,320
So he didn’t let me tell you.

106
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,520
He doesn’t want you to worry.

107
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,960
He went to every store

108
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,320
in the digital mall

109
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,600
and finally found it.

110
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,480
The master

111
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,640
is Captain Shu himself.

112
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,840
What do you mean?

113
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,000
Do you think I’m stupid?

114
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,440
Xia...

115
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:03,780
(Lu Feng)

116
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,440
Xia, I have something for you.

117
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:06,640
I sent it to the bar.

118
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,800
Go to get it tonight.

119
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,880
I don’t have time. Just leave it there.

120
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:20,960
No.

121
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,880
It’s fresh food. It will spoil
if you leave it there.

122
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,000
Just go get it.

123
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,520
I’ve told them about it.

124
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:35,840
Does your boss

125
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,160
have something for me?

126
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:37,960
Yes.

127
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:38,760
Well, Miss Ruan.

128
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,600
Have a seat.

129
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,280
I’ll get it.

130
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:40,820
Okay.

131
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:43,800
Here.

132
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,160
Come on.

133
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,360
Please.

134
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,520
I didn’t order it.

135
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:52,160
You only order this
every time you are here.

136
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,720
Our boss specially instructed us

137
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,760
to send you one for free.

138
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,080
Please enjoy it.

139
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,160
Thank you.

140
