It’s so romantic.

145
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:10,800
You...

146
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:14,280
Didn’t you go to Thailand?

147
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,360
I’m back.

148
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,080
What are you going to give me?

149
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,280
Just give it to me

150
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:22,560
and I’ll leave.

151
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,720
I want to give

152
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,440
myself to you.

153
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,400
Xia.

154
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,120
I’m here

155
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,440
to tell you

156
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,240
that I was attracted to you

157
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,680
from the first sight of you.

158
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,040
You are brave,

159
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,360
strong,

160
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,360
frank and cute.

161
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,640
There has never been a girl

162
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,320
who can attract all my attention

163
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,880
like you.

164
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,360
You flustered me

165
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,360
and that’s why I was so impulsive.

166
00:07:58,640 --> 00:07:59,440
I...

167
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,160
I don’t know what my chances

168
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,520
of success are in this way.

169
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,360
But I just want to

170
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,640
tell you directly,

171
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:09,960
I like you.

172
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,240
Be my girlfriend.

173
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:22,520
Say yes! Say yes!

174
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,720
Say yes! Say yes!

175
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,560
Say yes! Say yes!

176
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:30,640
Say yes! Say yes!

177
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,680
Say yes!

178
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,080
Lu Feng.

179
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:38,760
I’m sorry.

180
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,320
I always thought

181
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,120
a playboy like you

182
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,200
must do everything just for fun.

183
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:50,840
I didn’t expect you to be
so serious this time.

184
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,640
I want to thank you.

185
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:56,200
Thank you for liking me.

186
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,200
Thank you

187
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,000
for everything you did for me.

188
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,200
Thank you a lot.

189
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,640
But...

190
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:08,440
I...

191
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,880
I can’t accept you.

192
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:14,720
Because the person in my heart

193
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,800
is not you.

194
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,840
You are a very good person.

195
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,720
So I think

196
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,200
you deserve a girl

197
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,200
who will treat you

198
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,720
wholeheartedly.

199
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,120
So...

200
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:37,960
So I’m just

201
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,280
a nice guy to you.

202
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:42,920
I am sorry.

203
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:46,480
Is Shu Wenbo that good?

204
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:50,600
Do you

205
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,360
like him that much?

206
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,040
It has nothing to do with him.

207
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:00,560
A relationship is not
a multiple-choice question.

208
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,080
The answer is not fixed.

209
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,640
No one can be someone’s stand-in.

210
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:17,560
Keep the flowers for

211
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,360
the girl who deserves you.

212
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:37,680
You came early today.

213
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:40,520
Yeah.

214
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,880
I’m the one who waits for you
every time, right?

215
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,440
Let’s start.

216
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,320
What do we practice today? Side kick?

217
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:48,480
Okay.

218
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:51,440
Kick two targets.

219
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,160
Okay.

220
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,360
Come on.

221
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,600
Remember the key I told you.

222
00:10:58,920 --> 00:11:00,000
Your head must be clear.

223
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:01,840
Come on.

224
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,200
You are doing well. Come on.

225
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:05,280
Nice.

226
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,040
Come on.

227
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:08,160
Xia!

228
00:11:08,190 --> 00:11:08,800
Stop!

229
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,840
Stop! Stop! Stop!

230
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:11,920
Stop!

231
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,520
What are you doing?
Are you going to kill me?

232
00:11:14,680 --> 00:11:15,880
Yes, I want to kill you.

233
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,520
You rejected me

234
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:21,000
but you fixed the camera for me.

235
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,880
I...

236
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,640
What do you mean?

237
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:26,880
I don’t mean anything.

238
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,040
I just want to make you happy.

239
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,040
Make me happy?

240
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,080
Yes.

241
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,680
Don’t you think you are funny?

242
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,000
You made me cry

243
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,800
a lot of times.

244
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,160
Now you are telling me
that you want to make me happy.

245
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,080
Shu Wenbo,

246
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,880
why are you pretending to be a nice guy?

247
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:44,200
I’m not.

248
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,480
You are not?

249
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,160
Then what do you mean?

250
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,000
You told me

251
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:51,320
that we are good friends.

252
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:53,400
Then you clung to
your brother and told him

253
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:55,000
you like me.

254
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,480
You even want to give me to Lu Feng.

255
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:59,360
What are you taking me for?

256
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:01,200
A ball?

257
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,320
I’m not!

258
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,040
Then why are you

259
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,560
kicking me around?

260
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,320
Shu Wenbo.

261
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,120
I hate you.

262
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,480
Xia!

263
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,440
What’s wrong with you?

264
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:46,200
What happened?

265
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,110
-Are you okay?
-How did this happen?

266
00:12:47,130 --> 00:12:48,120
How are you?

267
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:49,160
-Are you all right?
-How are you?

268
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:49,920
It looks serious.

269
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,160
I don’t know. He is bleeding.

270
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:54,280
It looks like someone fell down.

271
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,000
Wake up.

272
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,280
He is bleeding.

273
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,040
Make a way.

274
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:58,880
Hurry up.

275
00:12:59,160 --> 00:13:00,040
Call an ambulance.

276
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:00,960
Hurry up.

277
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,040
He is bleeding from the head.

278
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,440
There may be a concussion.

279
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,280
Contact his family now.

280
00:13:06,330 --> 00:13:06,840
Okay.

281
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,240
Hello, is it the hospital?

282
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,520
Come on, hold him.

283
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,880
Put this under him.

284
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,160
Here.

285
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:19,480
I’m waiting for you at the door.
Have you arrived?

286
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:28,600
Hello, Uncle.

287
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:29,960
Xiaotong fell down.

288
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:32,040
We have called an ambulance.

289
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,000
Okay.

290
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,960
Come on, press it.

291
00:13:43,780 --> 00:13:49,420
(Shao Yuhan)

292
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:07,480
Excuse me!

293
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,720
Everyone, make a way!

